Whenever you use //Stamina// to pay for cost of using //Resist// you may reduce //Stamina// cost by one (e.g. 4:1 instead of 5:1). This stacks with other //Stamina// related talents (i.e. [[♣ Intense Study]], [[♣ Second Wind]], [[♣ Overtime]]), but cannot reduce the cost below 1.